io.zero88.jooqx.datatype

Interface UserTypeAsJooqType<V,J>

  • Type Parameters:
    V - Vert.x SQL data type
    J - The jOOQ data type and an user type - i.e. any type available from SQLDataType
    All Superinterfaces:
    org.jooq.Converter<J,J>, DataTypeMapper<V,J,J>, java.io.Serializable

    public interface UserTypeAsJooqType<V,J>
extends DataTypeMapper<V,J,J>
    It is short form of DataTypeMapper that means a record field is used user type as jOOQ data type
    See Also:
    DataTypeMapper, Converter
    API Note:
    In nutshell, it is equals with default JooqxConverter
